## 3.1 Basic Dataset Verification

Before writing the Abstract I needed to confirm the exact numbers I would
be reporting — total tracks, number of genres, and zero missing values in
the analytical columns. These details have to be precise in an abstract.

```{r dataset-verification}
core_features <- c("danceability", "energy", "loudness", "speechiness",
                   "acousticness", "instrumentalness", "liveness",
                   "valence", "tempo", "genre")

missing_check <- colSums(is.na(spotify_df[, core_features]))

